OL,3,CEbola cases pass 600 but global risk
OL,4,Cremains low, says WHO
OL,6,FThe risk of an Ebola outbreak is high
OL,7,Flocally but low on a global scale, the
OL,8,FWorld Health Organisation has said.
OL,10,FThere have been at least 139 suspected
OL,11,Fdeaths from the Ebola Bundibugyo virus
OL,12,Fand almost 600 suspected cases in and
OL,13,Faround the Democratic Republic of
OL,14,FCongo, director-general Tedros Adhanom
OL,15,FGhebreyesus said during a press
OL,16,Fconference on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
