OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779311467
OL,3,CEbola cases pass 600 but global risk
OL,4,Cremains low, says WHO
OL,6,F"We expect those numbers to keep
OL,7,Fincreasing, given the amount of time
OL,8,Fthe virus was circulating before the
OL,9,Foutbreak was detected," Ghebreyesus
OL,10,Ftold reporters.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FMore than 50 cases have been confirmed
OL,18,Fin Congo's northern provinces of Ituri
OL,19,Fand North Kivu, as well as two in
OL,20,FKampala, Uganda, including one death,
OL,21,Fhe said.
