CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779311467
OL,3,CEbola cases pass 600 but global risk
OL,4,Cremains low, says WHO
OL,6,FBunia residents have told how masks
OL,7,Fhave become harder to find and that
OL,8,Fsome disinfectants, previously sold
OL,9,Ffor 2,500 (81p) Congolese francs, now
OL,10,Fcost up to 10,000 francs (#3.25).
OL,12,F"It's truly sad and painful because
OL,13,Fwe've already been through a security
OL,14,Fcrisis, and now Ebola is here too,"
OL,15,Fsaid Justin Ndasi, a resident of Bunia.
OL,17,F"We have to protect ourselves to avoid
OL,18,Fthis epidemic."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
