OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779311467
OL,3,CEbola cases pass 600 but global risk
OL,4,Cremains low, says WHO
OL,6,FTrish Newport, emergency programme
OL,7,Fmanager from Doctors Without Borders
OL,8,Faid group, said her team in Bunia
OL,9,Fidentified suspected cases over the
OL,10,Fweekend in the Salama hospital, where
OL,11,Fthere is no isolation ward.
OL,13,FThey tried, unsuccessfully, to place
OL,14,Fthe patients in another health
OL,15,Ffacility in Bunia.
OL,17,F"Every health facility they called
OL,18,Fsaid, 'We're full of suspects cases.
OL,19,FWe don't have any space.' This gives
OL,20,Fyou a vision of how crazy it is right
OL,21,Fnow," Newport said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
